373
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,000
Huan's with them.

374
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:05,880
What's there to worry about?

375
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,680
You can't be so sure.

376
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:08,640
You know what?

377
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:10,960
Huan's mischievous.

378
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:11,759
I don't know
what Huaisong

379
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,799
did to her these days.

380
00:22:13,799 --> 00:22:14,680
She really

381
00:22:14,839 --> 00:22:16,000
adores him recently.

382
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:16,680
If we
help him accidentally,

383
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:19,480
it'd be terrible.

384
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,599
It can't be.

385
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,839
Shican, you're so naive!

386
00:22:25,839 --> 00:22:26,720
Listen.

387
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:27,920
Huaisong helped me
get my ID back,

388
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,599
But if I had to choose someone to help

389
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:31,880
between you and him,

390
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,640
I'm definitely on your side.

391
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,039
I won't lie to you!

392
00:22:38,359 --> 00:22:39,160
I'll leave the work to you.

393
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,400
Go for it, Shican!

394
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,440
Hurry up, boss.

395
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:47,079
The iron fireworks is starting soon!

396
00:22:47,319 --> 00:22:48,039
Okay.

397
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:53,519
Remember back in

398
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:54,799
high school,

399
00:22:54,799 --> 00:22:56,200
there was a snack street near our school?

400
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,480
A sugar painting artist
set up a stall

401
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,279
there occasionally.

402
00:23:02,079 --> 00:23:04,079
I remember there were lots of food stalls

403
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,960
but don't recall the sugar painting guy.

404
00:23:06,559 --> 00:23:07,160
I remember there was also...
Oh, right

405
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,359
I forgot you don't eat takeout,

406
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:11,119
and streetfood either, right?

407
00:23:12,279 --> 00:23:13,720
Not really. I...

408
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,200
Take it.

409
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,240
Thank you, sir.
You're welcome.

410
00:23:16,759 --> 00:23:17,799
What were you saying just now?

411
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,359
Where's Huan?

412
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,960
She was right here a second ago.

413
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,680
Maybe she went to watch the iron fireworks?

414
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:26,079
She knows this area
very well.

415
00:23:27,039 --> 00:23:27,839
Let's go find her.

416
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:28,839
Okay.
Huan!

417
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:30,160
Huan!

418
00:23:33,079 --> 00:23:33,880
Huan!

419
00:23:36,519 --> 00:23:37,119
Huan!

420
00:23:40,279 --> 00:23:41,160
- Huan!
- Excuse me.

421
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,359
Huan!

422
00:23:44,079 --> 00:23:45,440
Ma'am, have you seen

423
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,240
a girl?
Huan!

424
00:23:46,759 --> 00:23:47,279
No, I haven't.
No?

425
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,279
Thanks anyway.

426
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,319
Excuse me.

427
00:24:03,279 --> 00:24:04,160
Excuse me. I've to go this way.

428
00:24:07,039 --> 00:24:07,680
Huan!
Hello?

429
00:24:08,319 --> 00:24:09,240
[Ms. Ruan,]

430
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,680
[it's me. Huan's back home now.]

431
00:24:11,799 --> 00:24:13,000
[Wish you and Mr. Xu]

432
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,359
[enjoy your date.]

433
00:24:14,759 --> 00:24:16,079
Alright. Good to know she's back home safe.

434
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,319
Mrs. Zhao said Huan's already home,

435
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:21,839
and told us to enjoy our...

436
00:24:26,039 --> 00:24:27,240
Enjoy watching the iron fireworks.

437
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,799
Then let's...

438
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,319
enjoy it.

439
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,039
The iron fireworks is starting soon.

440
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,680
Let's count down

441
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:39,519
Go.

442
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:46,000
It's starting.

443
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:51,279
So big.

444
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,519
So beautiful!

445
00:25:11,519 --> 00:25:12,359
That's amazing.

446
00:25:19,599 --> 00:25:20,880
Really beautiful.

447
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:27,799
Bravo!

448
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,240
Sorry, ma'am.

449
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,400
I bumped into you.

450
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:52,480
N- no problem.

451
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,440
Sorry, sir.

452
00:29:22,319 --> 00:29:23,000
It doesn't matter.

453
00:29:53,279 --> 00:29:55,279
This is perfect.

454
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:59,319
Shican, hurry back.

455
00:29:59,319 --> 00:30:00,359
I've finished setting everything up.

456
00:30:00,359 --> 00:30:01,400
Mission accomplished.

457
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,000
It'll definitely make you succeed.

458
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:10,440
Shican, you're back.

459
00:30:10,759 --> 00:30:12,079
I just sent you a message.

460
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,599
Take a look. What do you think?

461
00:30:13,599 --> 00:30:14,519
Are you satisfied?

462
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:16,000
Look at these fairy lights,

463
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,000
and the little lanterns.

464
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,359
Doesn't it feel like spending New Year?

465
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:19,400
And look over there.

466
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:20,759
I prepared mixing console.

467
00:30:20,759 --> 00:30:21,640
When you sing tonight,
it'll have mixing effects.

468
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,200
We've got

469
00:30:23,519 --> 00:30:25,319
all the equipment ready. How's that?

470
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:26,680
No need for it.

471
00:30:32,119 --> 00:30:32,839
Take it all down.

472
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,000
What?

473
00:30:43,319 --> 00:30:44,400
What's wrong?

474
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,200
Come, quickly.

475
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:02,640
Hello?
Hello?

476
00:31:03,759 --> 00:31:04,519
Yu,

477
00:31:04,839 --> 00:31:06,119
come back quickly

478
00:31:06,119 --> 00:31:07,240
for Shican.

479
00:31:07,519 --> 00:31:08,519
What happened?

480
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:09,839
The thing is

481
00:31:09,839 --> 00:31:11,519
I don't know what's going on.

482
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:13,200
He went out earlier

483
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,359
and after he came back

484
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:16,480
he said the concert tonight is canceled.

485
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,799
Now he locked himself

486
00:31:17,799 --> 00:31:19,000
in his room.

487
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,039
I knocked several times

488
00:31:20,039 --> 00:31:21,000
but he wouldn't open.

489
00:31:21,279 --> 00:31:21,920
Okay, I see.
I'm coming back now.

490
00:31:22,839 --> 00:31:23,599
Okay.

491
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,160
Let's go back first

492
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:53,880
Shican, are you in there?

493
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,319
Shican.

494
00:32:06,599 --> 00:32:07,400
Shican?

495
00:32:09,279 --> 00:32:11,799
I'm... I'm sleeping.

496
00:32:14,599 --> 00:32:15,680
You're still lying

497
00:32:16,279 --> 00:32:17,880
as clumsily as back then.

498
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,119
What's wrong?
Didn't he join

499
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,119
the singing competition?

500
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:36,279
He performed his original song

501
00:32:36,279 --> 00:32:37,400
and just now the result came out.

502
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,200
He didn't make it.

503
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:39,920
You know

504
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,119
original songs usually are

505
00:32:41,119 --> 00:32:42,279
at a disadvantage in competitions.

506
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:44,000
He must be dispirited.

507
00:32:53,039 --> 00:32:54,920
Shican, are you in there?

508
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,319
Shican?

509
00:33:02,559 --> 00:33:03,519
I...

510
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,559
I'm... sleeping.

511
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,519
Sleeping in the

512
00:33:11,519 --> 00:33:12,680
rehearsal room?

513
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,400
With such a lame excuse

514
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,519
you think you can fool me?

515
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:21,720
Shican,

516
00:33:22,279 --> 00:33:24,599
did something happen?

517
00:33:25,359 --> 00:33:26,480
Wanna talk about it with me?

518
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,319
Can I come in?

519
00:33:42,759 --> 00:33:43,319
Please come in.

520
00:33:55,359 --> 00:33:56,319
Let me get you some water.

521
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:11,280
Thanks.

522
00:34:14,719 --> 00:34:16,880
Your agent seems to be looking for you.

523
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:24,400
Shican, you've got the nerve

524
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,519
to go out without a mask

525
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:26,400
or hat?
The whole day...

526
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:33,000
You were taken secret photos?

527
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:35,599
It's my fault.

528
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,280
I was in such a hurry to leave

529
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,360
and forgot I'm a star.

530
00:34:40,559 --> 00:34:41,440
But it's okay.

531
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:43,559
I went outside alone anyway.

532
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,480
Then why is your agent

533
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,800
so angry?

534
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,360
Over the years,

535
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,920
we have conflicts more and more

536
00:34:58,599 --> 00:34:59,719
due to our different personal beliefs.

537
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:01,920
The slightest thing

538
00:35:02,119 --> 00:35:02,960
will make him furious.

539
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,760
This time I came to Shen'ao,

540
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,679
it's like a vacation

541
00:35:06,679 --> 00:35:07,960
I arranged for myself.

542
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:09,960
He thinks I'm too willful.

543
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:13,800
Am I really

544
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:16,599
that willful?

545
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:26,360
But chasing dreams

546
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:27,920
sometimes requires

547
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:28,960
to be a little willful, doesn't it?

548
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:34,000
Actually,

549
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,199
you came here this time

550
00:35:35,199 --> 00:35:36,519
not to have dinner with me,

551
00:35:37,119 --> 00:35:38,360
nor for Shishan.

552
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,119
You just wanted to get some air,

553
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,480
to rediscover

554
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:43,599
your songwriting inspiration, right?

555
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:45,679
Right, kind of.

556
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,679
In this case,

557
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,280
as a singer,

558
00:35:52,519 --> 00:35:54,039
to rediscover your songwriting original aspiration

559
00:35:54,039 --> 00:35:55,079
by taking a willful break

560
00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:56,199
is nothing wrong.

561
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:59,239
But my agent always says

562
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,360
I have to do things

563
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,519
I don't want to do.

564
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,159
Or I'll lose the chance

565
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,079
to do what I want.

566
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:06,960
Then what is it
that you want to do?

567
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:10,920
Standing on stage,

568
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:13,000
singing songs I wrote myself.

569
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,440
What if

570
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:17,480
you have to shorten

571
00:36:17,719 --> 00:36:18,960
what you just said?

572
00:36:20,599 --> 00:36:21,599
Say it again then?

573
00:36:23,880 --> 00:36:25,079
Sing my own songs.

574
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:30,400
See,

575
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,079
you've already figured it out.

576
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,679
You...

577
00:37:24,079 --> 00:37:25,400
What are you doing here?

578
00:37:26,199 --> 00:37:27,000
Practicing boxing.

579
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:33,119
Not bad.

580
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,559
I'm going down now.

581
00:37:37,599 --> 00:37:38,880
Are you gonna keep practicing here?

582
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:40,760
Doing it downstairs then.

583
00:37:48,519 --> 00:37:49,360
Practicing boxing?

584
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:53,559
[If the things]

585
00:37:53,559 --> 00:37:55,079
[you don't want to do]

586
00:37:55,519 --> 00:37:56,559
[make you forget]

587
00:37:56,559 --> 00:37:57,719
[your original aspiration for music,]

588
00:37:58,159 --> 00:37:59,880
[then will you be happy]

589
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,480
[even if you stand on stage?]

590
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,599
[Will the fans who truly like you]

591
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,599
[be happy about it?]

592
00:38:18,719 --> 00:38:19,400
Shican,

593
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,679
I understand how you feel now.

594
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,360
But you keep locking yourself

595
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,360
in this room.

596
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:27,320
Are you giving up singing?

597
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:34,400
Maybe my parents were right.

598
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,719
I really don't have what it takes to sing.

599
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,440
Yu,

600
00:38:44,119 --> 00:38:44,920
I'm sorry

601
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,559
to let you all down.

602
00:38:49,559 --> 00:38:50,800
As to whether you have what it takes,

603
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,199
an outsider like me

604
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:53,400
can't say for sure.

605
00:38:54,719 --> 00:38:55,440
But how come you said

606
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,639
you've let us down?

607
00:39:03,599 --> 00:39:04,920
I failed to take the guitar

608
00:39:05,559 --> 00:39:06,920
to a bigger stage,

609
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:10,119
and make it worth its price.

610
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,480
When you walked into the guitar shop,

611
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,400
did you do it to stand on stage

612
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,480
and become a big star?

613
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,000
I didn't think that much before.

614
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,079
I just wanted to sing.

615
00:39:26,159 --> 00:39:27,400
Then the moment you picked it up

616
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,480
and sang,

617
00:39:29,519 --> 00:39:30,719
wasn't it already worth it?

618
00:39:40,679 --> 00:39:41,480
Shican,

619
00:39:42,119 --> 00:39:43,000
looks like

620
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,599
you've been saved again.

621
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:07,239
What are you looking at?

622
00:40:09,199 --> 00:40:09,920
Shican,

623
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:12,159
you're feeling better now?

624
00:40:16,519 --> 00:40:17,320
Good.

625
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,239
So when you were in the room just now,

626
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:20,239
you...

627
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:23,480
Did you confess to Yu?

628
00:40:26,119 --> 00:40:26,800
No.

629
00:40:27,199 --> 00:40:28,320
You didn't.

630
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,719
Then how did she

631
00:40:30,719 --> 00:40:31,679
cheer you up?

632
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,599
She didn't helped me purposely.

633
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,119
But by accident,

634
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:40,800
she cured my another problem.

635
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,440
That's it?

636
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:50,840
The moon is in the sky.

637
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:52,719
You can't own it.

638
00:40:53,559 --> 00:40:55,119
But standing where it shines on you

639
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,559
is also kind of possessing of it,

640
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,079
isn't it?

641
00:41:04,639 --> 00:41:05,239
Right.

642
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,280
Then Shican,

643
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:11,559
are we still taking down the stage?

644
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:17,239
No.

645
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,480
[Where Shican is standing]

646
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:29,920
[looks so lively.]

647
00:41:37,079 --> 00:41:37,760
Well,

648
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:40,280
everyone's busy with their New Year celebrations.

649
00:41:42,119 --> 00:41:43,199
[What are you doing?]

650
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:50,199
Nothing, just bored.

651
00:41:50,199 --> 00:41:51,480
You know

652
00:41:51,480 --> 00:41:53,119
my family gets quiet and cold

653
00:41:53,119 --> 00:41:54,280
during festivals.

654
00:41:55,199 --> 00:41:57,199
[Me too.]

655
00:41:58,000 --> 00:41:58,960
[Let's play a couple of games.]

656
00:42:00,679 --> 00:42:01,760
You have so many people at home,

657
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:02,639
and you're still bored?

658
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,199
[They're all outside having fun.]

659
00:42:06,519 --> 00:42:07,639
[I didn't go out as it's cold.]

660
00:42:12,199 --> 00:42:13,480
Alright then, log in.

661
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,440
Yi!

662
00:42:19,559 --> 00:42:20,320
Don't stay in your room alone
at the New Year's Eve.

663
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:21,760
Okay?

664
00:42:22,079 --> 00:42:22,760
Come out quickly!

665
00:42:22,840 --> 00:42:23,880
Chat with

666
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,559
your grandparents.

667
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,920
There are so many people.

668
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:27,960
They don't need me.

669
00:42:28,719 --> 00:42:30,159
Your phone needs you more?

670
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,039
I'm not playing my phone.

671
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:33,559
Hurry up!

672
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:51,159
Someone on my phone needs me.

673
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:53,760
[Just got a new message.]

674
00:42:54,159 --> 00:42:55,320
[Shican is holding]

675
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:56,199
[a small]

676
00:42:56,199 --> 00:42:57,360
[charity concert]

677
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,360
[in Shen'ao tonight.]

678
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,119
Did you tap to record?

679
00:43:02,239 --> 00:43:03,679
Yes, record it.

680
00:43:03,679 --> 00:43:05,159
Record, right. Start it.

681
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:06,599
Okay.
It's starting.

682
00:43:10,639 --> 00:43:12,800
One two, one two, one two three!

683
00:43:13,119 --> 00:43:14,079
Testing, testing.

684
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:16,320
Okay.

685
00:43:16,519 --> 00:43:17,719
No.

686
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:18,880
Alright, stop wasting time.

687
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:19,880
- Hurry up and start.
- Enough!

688
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:21,000
Okay.

689
00:43:22,039 --> 00:43:24,159
Alright, I'm starting.

690
00:43:25,199 --> 00:43:26,039
Hello,

691
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:27,880
dear friends and family,

692
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:29,599
and community neighbors.

693
00:43:29,599 --> 00:43:30,239
Great!

694
00:43:31,800 --> 00:43:33,159
I'm Li Shishan,

695
00:43:33,159 --> 00:43:35,800
tonight's MC!

696
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:36,239
What?

697
00:43:37,239 --> 00:43:38,000
Host?
MC means

698
00:43:38,559 --> 00:43:39,280
the host!

699
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:40,559
The host!

700
00:43:41,039 --> 00:43:42,000
Clap your hands!

701
00:43:43,440 --> 00:43:44,719
Thank Ms. Ruan, the famous writer,

702
00:43:44,719 --> 00:43:45,679
for translating for me!

703
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:47,000
Needs a translator, huh?

704
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:49,559
I'm so glad everyone

705
00:43:49,559 --> 00:43:51,360
came to my courtyard.

706
00:43:52,360 --> 00:43:54,880
On this New Year's Eve,

707
00:43:55,039 --> 00:43:56,239
let's enjoy

708
00:43:56,239 --> 00:43:58,239
a unique

709
00:43:58,239 --> 00:43:59,599
concert together.

710
00:43:59,760 --> 00:44:01,639
Alright, I'll stop talking.

711
00:44:01,880 --> 00:44:03,159
Let's welcome tonight's

712
00:44:03,159 --> 00:44:05,039
the honored guest,

713
00:44:05,079 --> 00:44:09,280
the famous singer Li Shican!

714
00:44:15,199 --> 00:44:16,400
Now let's welcome Shican

715
00:44:16,639 --> 00:44:18,239
to sing a new song for us!

716
00:44:25,199 --> 00:44:27,159
Hello, everyone, I'm Li Shican.

717
00:44:27,760 --> 00:44:29,239
Maybe many of you here

718
00:44:29,239 --> 00:44:30,400
haven't known me yet.

719
00:44:30,480 --> 00:44:31,199
But on this day

720
00:44:31,199 --> 00:44:32,679
of family joy,

721
00:44:32,679 --> 00:44:33,880
you came here

722
00:44:34,280 --> 00:44:35,519
and gave me

723
00:44:35,519 --> 00:44:36,639
such warm applause.

724
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:38,079
Thank you all for being here.

725
00:44:44,360 --> 00:44:45,960
Shen'ao is a truly

726
00:44:46,199 --> 00:44:47,320
magical town.

727
00:44:47,679 --> 00:44:49,039
Since I arrived here,

728
00:44:49,039 --> 00:44:51,199
time seems to have slowed down.

729
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:53,880
There are no stage lights on me.

730
00:44:54,119 --> 00:44:54,760
No eyes around me

731
00:44:54,760 --> 00:44:56,079
watching me.

732
00:44:56,679 --> 00:44:58,079
I feel like I'm back to be

733
00:44:58,679 --> 00:45:00,239
the one who only

734
00:45:00,840 --> 00:45:02,480
care about writing songs.

735
00:45:08,679 --> 00:45:09,800
After today,

736
00:45:09,880 --> 00:45:11,280
I'm leaving this place.

737
00:45:12,159 --> 00:45:13,239
When I leave,

738
00:45:13,480 --> 00:45:14,760
I will be different version of myself.

739
00:45:15,480 --> 00:45:18,199
I'll become my old self

740
00:45:19,159 --> 00:45:20,880
and return

741
00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:23,199
the dazzling world full of challenges.

742
00:45:24,239 --> 00:45:25,920
So I want to perform

743
00:45:26,239 --> 00:45:27,679
a song I wrote here

744
00:45:27,679 --> 00:45:28,679
for all of you

745
00:45:28,760 --> 00:45:29,639
at my last night here.

746
00:45:30,679 --> 00:45:32,159
This song isn't just mine.

747
00:45:32,679 --> 00:45:33,800
It belongs to Shen'ao

748
00:45:34,679 --> 00:45:35,920
and all of you

749
00:45:38,559 --> 00:45:39,400
here tonight.

750
00:45:39,800 --> 00:45:41,679
Bravo!
